Section 5: Rank Expand Special Markdown Syntax

The Rank Expand system uses custom shortcodes that your WordPress
theme/plugin must render.

  -------------------------- --------------------------------------------
  **Syntax**                 **What It Renders**

  (call: )                   Click-to-call button with tracking number

  (cta: call)                Call Now CTA block

  (cta: estimate)            Free Estimate CTA block

  (cta: book)                Book Appointment CTA block

  (offer: contact-now)       Contact form with special offer messaging

  (element: services)        Dynamic services grid widget

  (element: locations)       Dynamic locations map/list widget

  (image: filename.webp)     Image placeholder for manual insertion

  {{ phone }}                Replaced with CallRail tracking number

  {{ location }}             Replaced with target neighborhood name
  -------------------------- --------------------------------------------

